        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Streamlining IRS Operations Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Internal Revenue Service to require that any tax return that is prepared electronically, but is printed and filed on paper, bear a code that can convert such return to an electronic format when scanned.</p>]]>
        </text>
